  "description": {
    "zh": "你好，我的朋友。我想，你已经听说过灯塔的那位商人了吧。我想做点什么，怎么说呢...我想亲自和他接触一下。不，现在还不是我们面对面接触的时候。而且，说实在话，我也不想离开我的老窝。但这样会有一个问题：对讲机信号根本没法从这里发射到灯塔去。你能找一些元件，让我组装一个信号发射器吗？",
    "en": "Hello, friend. I guess you've heard about the trader at the Lighthouse. I've got a little ambition, so to speak... I want to get in touch with him personally. No, it's still a long way to go before we meet face to face. And I don't like to leave my lair, honestly. There's a problem: the radio signal can't reach the lighthouse from here. Can you find the parts so I can put together a signal transmitter?"
  },
